st for future calculations\nof larger nuclei or finite temperature nuclear matter using path integral\nquantum Monte Carlo.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Jul 2022 00:47:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Jul 2022 02:35:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-19"}
